flowchart TD
    A[Reconciliation break detected] --> B{Customer impact?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Assess severity and financial impact]
    B -->|No| D[Classify operational category]

    C --> E{Financial correction required?}
    E -->|Yes| F[Calculate adjustment and validate population]
    E -->|No| G[Prepare customer communication if needed]

    D --> H[Identify source system and comparison system]
    H --> I{Timing issue?}
    I -->|Yes| J[Monitor until SLA or settlement window closes]
    I -->|No| K[Investigate root cause]

    F --> L[Resolve break]
    G --> L
    J --> L
    K --> L

    L --> M[Log root cause]
    M --> N[Add prevention control]
    N --> O[Close break]